Site owner has copied my blog post without my permission. check below few paragraph which is copied illegally.

"www.apgenco.gov.in is the official site from where you can download your APGENCO Hall Ticket for Recruitment 2012 of AE and SE Engineering post in various division."

"Andhra Pradesh Power Generation Corporation Limited (APGENCO) is likely issue the Hall Tickets for Sub Engineers (SE) and Assistant Engineers  (AE) recruitment for all those candidates who applied for written test."

"In case you don’t received or missed or even lost your APGENCO Hall Tickets 2012 then candidates can download it under the career and job page of website by entering your date of birth and application form number."
